      "content": "That makes sense. I'm particularly curious about the \"creeping\" part you mentioned with the enforcement timeline. If these small, unauthorized additions or secondary uses keep slowly expanding or moving into the restricted zones over several years, how does the city distinguish between a single violation and a series of increasingly disruptive, unexpected intrusions? Does the city have a way to deal with these types of persistent, small-scale encroachments that seem to multiply or spread throughout a local area?",
